u32 XLlFifo::BaseAddress

u32 XLlFifo::Datainterface
 

Data interface of the FIFO. This value is zero if the Datainterface is AXI4-lite.

u32 XLlFifo::IsReady
 

IsReady is non-zero if the driver instance has been initialized.
